This method worked perfectly.

i have two ejb schedulers inside a class running on a weblogic server. it works fine except in some rare occasions where one of them (the first timer) does not even trigger, while the other one is working. i get aware of it by looking at server logs and see no logs available for it. i wonder why it never gets triggered!

the problem is solved by restarting the server node on which the timers are working on. 
