```kotlin
data class N(
    @field:Min(value = 0, message = &quot;id must be positive.&quot;)
    val id: Long? = null,

    @field:NotNull
    @field:Size(min = 2, max = 32, message = &quot;wrong size: should be 32 chars long.&quot;)
    val token: String? = null
)
```

